#### Feature Description

I want to be able to call a function of the Component the Bottom Sheet was called from.

For example, Ionic has methods as parameters of a Modal Instance:

    `
        openModal(item) {
            const modal = this.modalCtrl.create(ModalComponent, {
              someModalMethod: (parameter) => {
